The `LinkDepartmentsSheet` uses a Sheet component (Radix UI) that renders an overlay with `pointer-events: auto` and a high `z-index`, blocking clicks on `sonner` toaster's "Cross [x]" and other page elements when open. The modal behavior of the `Sheet` prevents background interactions, and the toaster’s `z-index` may be too low. This causes only sidebar buttons to remain interactive.

